name: "Mosh Bug" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson
description: [Crayon on cardboard with baby slobber, digital embellishments, and moshing.] Evil bug drawn on cardboard by me, then chewed up an slobbered on by my granddaughter, Felicity, then photographed, digitally freaked out, and moshed. ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Granddaughter)
